description:
Whether you’re curious about drawing or want to further develop your talents, this workshop will provide the chance to learn new skills and engage with the museum’s collection. Materials are provided, as is supportive instruction.

See all upcoming sketch classes and workshops. For additional information, please call (312) 443-3680 or email museum-programs@artic.edu. Classes are recommended for ages 16 and up.

Persons with disabilities who would like to request an accessibility accommodation for an Art Institute program are encouraged to send an e-mail to access@artic.edu as far in advance as possible.
